quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"Ne obulamu bwokhushialo buno shini eshindu tawe halali amakhuwa kabulamwo oluchendo nende omubayo sa. Ne obulamu bwomwikulu nibwo obulamu bwatoto, bamanyangakhwo!"
  29,65,"Ne nibanina muliaro (Munyanza), balaamanga Nyasaye mubutswenufu. Ne niyakhamala okhubahabina nibakhoola khulukongo, olwenolo bachaka okhumutsokaasia."
  29,66,"Khobanyoole okhubula okhupa orio khukakhwabahelesia mbu khobekhoye, halali ahambi hano balamanya."
  29,67,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu efwe khwakhola eshialo shiabu okhuba shioluyali nende omulembe, ne Abandu bayuulungwa mumbeka mwabu? Koo, basuubilanga obushiamu, ne emikabo chia Nyasaye nichio chia bakhayanga?"
  29,68,"Ne ni wina omubii muno oyo okhushila ulia uchishila Nyasaye obubeyi, nohomba ukhaya obwatoto nibumalile okhumuulila? Koo, Jahanam shinishio shakhabe eshimenyo shabakhayi?"
  29,69,"Ne balia bakhalabananga okhubeela efwe, toto abo khulabalunjisia khutsinjila tsiefu. Ne toto Nyasaye ali halala nende bakholanga amalayi."
  30,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim."
  30,2,"Abarumi bashilwa (nende Abafarisayo khumyero)."
  30,3,"Mushialo shili ahambi (nende Ebufarisayo), nabo olunyuma lwa okhushilwa khwabu okho bakhashile."
  30,4,"Khu mika mititi butswa. Likhuwa nilia Nyasaye, lieyinyuma nende lieyimbeli. Ne inyanga eyo Abasuubili balisaangala."
  30,5,"Khubuhabini bwa Nyasaye. Ahabinanga wayenya. Naye niwa Amaani muno, Owetsimbabaasi po."